{"answer":"The Vitamin D3 (cholecalciferol) consolidation proposals for ingredient group 1 have strong evidence, with both Prinova USA and PureBulk recommended as suppliers. Each can serve 21 of 21 companies, covering 21 SKUs, with an estimated savings of 30.0% and a confidence level of 61% [P1][P2]. The primary risk associated with these proposals is \"single-supplier concentration risk,\" meaning reliance on a single supplier could pose a risk if there are disruptions in their supply chain [P1][P2].","citations":[{"doc_id":"P1","kind":"proposal","label":"Proposal #1 — Prinova USA","url":"","proposal_id":1,"meta":{"proposal_id":1,"ingredient_group_id":1,"supplier_id":27,"supplier_name":"Prinova USA","priority":"HIGH","confidence":61.2,"savings_pct":30.0}},{"doc_id":"P2","kind":"proposal","label":"Proposal #2 — PureBulk","url":"","proposal_id":2,"meta":{"proposal_id":2,"ingredient_group_id":1,"supplier_id":28,"supplier_name":"PureBulk","priority":"HIGH","confidence":61.2,"savings_pct":30.0}}],"retrieved":[{"doc_id":"P1","kind":"proposal","score":0.4731,"label":"Proposal #1 — Prinova USA","url":"","proposal_id":1},{"doc_id":"P2","kind":"proposal","score":0.4729,"label":"Proposal #2 — PureBulk","url":"","proposal_id":2},{"doc_id":"P10","kind":"proposal","score":0.4515,"label":"Proposal #10 — Prinova USA","url":"","proposal_id":10},{"doc_id":"P11","kind":"proposal","score":0.4441,"label":"Proposal #11 — PureBulk","url":"","proposal_id":11},{"doc_id":"P28","kind":"proposal","score":0.4127,"label":"Proposal #28 — Prinova USA","url":"","proposal_id":28},{"doc_id":"E12","kind":"evidence","score":0.4096,"label":"Evidence (product 3, product_scrape)","url":"https://www.iherb.com/pr/p/71022","proposal_id":null},{"doc_id":"E3","kind":"evidence","score":0.4064,"label":"Evidence (product 2, product_scrape)","url":"https://www.iherb.com/pr/p/116514","proposal_id":null},{"doc_id":"E13","kind":"evidence","score":0.4063,"label":"Evidence (product 13, product_scrape)","url":"https://